<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About - Share Pad</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page-content">
    <div class="about-header">
      <h1>About Share Pad</h1>
      <p>A notepad you can reach from memory. No links to copy, no messages to send. Just type a simple URL and start writing.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="features">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>The Idea</h3>
        <p>Sometimes you need to move text between devices but can't send yourself a link. Share Pad gives every pad a short, human-readable URL you can just type in.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>Easy to Remember</h3>
        <p>Pads live at simple addresses like sharepad/johannes or sharepad/shopping-list. No random characters, no codes to memorize.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>Works Anywhere</h3>
        <p>Open any browser, type your pad name, and your notes are there. No app to install, no account to create.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>No Sign-Up</h3>
        <p>Just pick a name for your pad and start writing. No registration, no email, no password. It just works.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <nav class="nav-bar">
    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <a href="/about" class="active">About</a>
  </nav>
</body>
</html>
